                            <comment id="14087285" author="remkop@yahoo.com" created="Wed, 6 Aug 2014 05:40:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The Commons Logging API classes are not included in the Log4j2 distribution by design. Users need to get those separately. If you use Maven it will pull in the necessary dependencies automatically. Otherwise you need to do this manually.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We will update the Usage and Requirements pages to be more clear about this.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14087686" author="remkop@yahoo.com" created="Wed, 6 Aug 2014 13:56:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Changed documentation to mention that the Commons Logging jar is required in revisions 1616234 and 1616235.&lt;br/&gt;
Please verify and close.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
